type.description:
### ⚠️ Requires [Mob Origins](https://moborigins.ultrusmods.me/en/latest/) to be installed! ⚠️

## Set Freeze Ticks

---

Sets the freeze ticks of an entity.

---

### Example
```json
{
    "type": "moborigins:set_freeze_ticks",
    "ticks": 20
}
```
Sets the freeze ticks of an entity to 20 ticks.
